{"tid":877112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"退休警司朱經緯刑滿出獄","createTime":"2018-10-26T06:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T06:05:53.000Z","uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8ad94e3851605020350e524d6a74f23367a8178a","tid":877112,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】因用警棍襲擊途人而被判囚三個月的退休警司朱經緯，早上刑滿出獄。<br />\n<br />\n服刑完畢的朱經緯早上約九時半離開赤柱監獄，親友及支持者迎接並鼓掌，有人與他擁抱及送上鮮花。<br />\n<br />\n朱經緯於2014年佔領運動期間，於旺角以警棍襲擊途人，被裁定一項「襲擊致造成身體傷害罪」罪成，判囚三個月。他被高等法院駁回上訴後即時服刑，至今刑滿出獄。他已向終審法院申請上訴，正等候排期聆訊。<br />\n<br />\nSource:- <a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E5%88%91%E6%BB%BF%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84-043958301.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%259C%25B1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25B7%25AF%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258D%2584-043958301.html&d=o9ODwADp1XMLi3ieOJp2c%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=313ee584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E5%88%91%E6%BB%BF%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84-043958301.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知朱sir d 棍法有冇更上一層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}